FitTrend strives to help you achieve your health and fitness goals. FitTrend supports many smartwatches, fitness trackers, scales, and other devices to take the manual work out of tracking your progress.

FitTrend can quickly and easily show your progress from different sources in one place to explore, visualize, and share. Whether you go it alone or team up with others, FitTrend wants to make your personal journey fun!
